Description_lang: Swear your oath to the Primalists to become Marked by Frost, increasing your Critical Strike by [medium amount]. Fighting alongside allies who are Marked by Earth or Fire has a chance to grant you half of their Mark's stats for $s1 seconds.
AuraDescription_lang: Critical Strike increased by $w1. Dealing harmful spells and abilities has a chance to grant you an additional ${$w1/2} Versatility or Haste if any nearby allies are Marked by Earth or Fire.
